{"tid":1542253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"睇見啲大陸人係墻入面用內聯網睇連登敢怒不能言就覺得好笑","createTime":"2019-09-04T19:56:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T04:05:36.000Z","uid":156363,"like":81,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"2cf79ffafa6e590b661c413f6125a878ffde5dc7","tid":1542253,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T19:56:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7DhVSgb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7DhVSgb.jpg&h=a02bdae0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多大陸韭菜冇得翻墻，接收境外消息都要搵人有限度轉載<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇到咩內容好睇施捨果條友俾啲咩內容佢睇。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個井口幾大就以為個天空有幾大。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇完仲要冇辦法參與我哋嘅討論，就算識翻墻連登account都係拎唔到，只可以係大陸個內聯網入面同班生蕃一齊圍爐取暖繼續鳩叫。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>係啊，無錯就係笑緊你啊。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>你覺唔覺得自己好似動物園啲黑猩猩咁？？隔住塊單向透視玻璃，入面嘅動物唔知出面嘅人望緊你，其實想話俾你聽你哋連打飛機出面嘅人都睇得清清楚楚囉。</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">等你進化咗識用連登先同我講嘢啦</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40a6e24fe020ff5d4b5a0ed888449a6195a0c431","tid":1542253,"uid":4596,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T20:18:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">垃圾支那賤畜</span></span>"},{"pid":"b0d7c638486dfa04e1148e70589522ed897f7da3","tid":1542