304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T20:57:01.000Z","msg":"有冇見過兇殺案由政府新聞處公佈？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1535010\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1535010</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n睇埋回覆先留言，因為分析我放咗喺回覆<br />\n<br />\n成個熱門勁多都係講林鄭撤回嘅風，<br />\n但而家佢撤唔撤回都好，831太子站有冇死人、有冇極嚴重傷勢受害人，呢d都係要查啊！唔好俾佢轉移焦點啊！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">好認真，點解一路發生咁多件事，都冇話撤回，突然今日會講起？到底呢幾日發生咗咩事逼到佢要做野？係咪真係其實死咗人？就算冇死人，到底情況係幾嚴重？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要求黨鐵交出831太子站完整CCTV記錄啊！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"52cf5c83665e25f1d384027908593e8d7a119341","tid":1542253,"uid":156363,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T21:16:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jtsbrfa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJtsbrfa.jpg&h=2695fef3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"47e611a8adb48671dc92d6b0263b0d5bff42abe8","tid":1542253,"uid":120431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T21:21:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2d5f94bb6311e13226e9bc5da95be830abb93ad","tid":1542253,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T21:27:31.000Z","msg":"现在是网络时代，别以为弄几个假消息就可以骗人<br />\n回复来自iPhone客户端38楼2019-09-04 23:45<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08f679e117ea2dc7b8bbfc275e5986652ba60ec2","tid":1542253,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T21:30:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd353252c76199cdb6c30fff216c271c8b7de5a8","tid":1542253,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T03:18:02.00